description: Demolition of existing buildings. Erection of buildings between four and sixteen-storeys in height to provide 10,500 sq.m. of B1 floorspace (office, research and development, and light industry), 209 residential units, retail, caf/restaurant (260m2) and crche/nursery (146m2 D1) uses with 120 parking spaces within the basement and provision of new public routes/spaces.
